### Visual Brand

- **Primary colors:** Black (#0f0f0f), Yellow/Gold (#FFD600 primary, #c8a84b gold accent), White (#ffffff)
- **Background:** Off-white (#f7f6f4), Charcoal for dark sections
- **Typography:** Font "Melody" (custom, hosted on HubSpot CDN), fallback to system sans-serif
